<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id14d223f8-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d" identifier="/us/usc/t21/s2014"><num value="2014">§ 2014.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading>
<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are authorized to be appropriated—</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id14d223f9-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d" identifier="/us/usc/t21/s2014/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><chapeau> for fiscal year 2007—</chapeau><subparagraph style="-uslm-lc:I13" class="indent2" id="id14d223fa-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d" identifier="/us/usc/t21/s2014/1/A"><num value="A">(A)</num><content> $500,000 to establish the NMIC and Council; and</content>
</subparagraph>
<subparagraph style="-uslm-lc:I13" class="indent2" id="id14d223fb-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d" identifier="/us/usc/t21/s2014/1/B"><num value="B">(B)</num><content> such sums as are necessary for the operation of the NMIC and Council; and</content>
</subparagraph>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id14d223fc-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d" identifier="/us/usc/t21/s2014/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> for each of fiscal years 2008 and 2009, such sums as are necessary for the operation of the NMIC and Council.</content>
</paragraph>
<sourceCredit id="id14d223fd-3a70-11f1-b089-c1e1e512a22d">(<ref href="/us/pl/109/469/tX/s1005">Pub. L. 109–469, title X, § 1005</ref>, <date date="2006-12-29">Dec. 29, 2006</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/120/3539">120 Stat. 3539</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
